Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(285,332)\fs16\fsp2}Level5
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且  本计划的原型是超电磁炮御阪美琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(368,332)\fs16\fsp2}Railgun
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:18:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻某处正在进行制造超能力者复制人的计划
