Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们的平均性能只有异能力的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(373,332)\fs16\fsp2}Level2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是强大的个体也无法超过强能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(435,332)\fs16\fsp2}Level3
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说只能制造出我的劣化版？
