Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(372,332)\fs16\fsp2}Sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
